{"word":"G2518 - καθεύδω - katheúdō - kath-yoo'-do - Sleep","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καθεύδω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katheúdō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kath-yoo'-do</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sleep</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நித்திரையாயிரு, நித்திரைபண்ணு, தூங்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to fall asleep, to drop off to sleep"},{"paragraph":"2. to sleep"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <b>&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x0301;&#x03B4;&#x03C9;</b> <b>heudo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>sleep</i>); to lie <i>down</i> to <i>rest</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>fall asleep</i> (literally or figuratively): - (be a-) sleep.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}